setupJacksonAnnotatedCommandSerializationAndDeserialization

public static <T extends Command> void setupJacksonAnnotatedCommandSerializationAndDeserialization(com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper mapper,
                                                                                                   Class<T> commandSubclassKlass)
Setup serialization and deserialization for Jackson-annotated Command subclasses. All Jackson-annotated Command subclasses must derive from a single base class.

The following is supported: 

     Object
     +-- CMD_BASE
         +-- CMD_0
         +-- CMD_1
And the following is not supported: 
     Object
     +-- CMD_0
     +-- CMD_1
See RaftAgent for more on which Command types are supported.

Parameters:
mapper - instance of ObjectMapper with which the serialization/deserialization mapping is registered
commandSubclassKlass - the base class of all the Jackson-annotated Command classes
See Also:
RaftAgent

setupCustomCommandSerializationAndDeserialization

public static void setupCustomCommandSerializationAndDeserialization(com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper mapper,
                                                                     CommandSerializer commandSerializer,
                                                                     CommandDeserializer commandDeserializer)
Setup custom serialization and deserialization for POJO Command subclasses.

See RaftAgent for more on which Command types are supported.

Parameters:
mapper - instance of ObjectMapper with which the serialization/deserialization mapping is registered
commandSerializer - instance of CommandSerializer that can serialize a POJO Command instance into binary
commandDeserializer - instance of CommandDeserializer that can deserialize binary into a POJO Command instance
See Also:
RaftAgent
